{"tid":1653612,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳： 真香港人認證圖 看懂了，但笑不出！ - 李八方","createTime":"2019-10-14T07:12:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T07:12:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ded86b96cf417aae41d7a2028328c454b2fbe8e8","tid":1653612,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:12:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20191014/20786573\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191014%2F20786573&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAtLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=30ce064f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191014%2F20786573&h=026c9e41\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20191014/20786573</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：<br />\n真香港人認證圖 看懂了，但笑不出！ - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191014/large/1570982744_5434.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191014%2Flarge%2F1570982744_5434.gif&h=3a40b110&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由6月到10月，「自殺」率大增。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人經歷過2019的自由之夏，從此不再一樣，抗爭生活已變日常，有網民製作咗「真‧香港人一定看懂的十幅圖」，將6月同10月唔同社會環境同現象做比較，如果全部睇得明，就係百分百真‧香港人，但如果一幅都睇唔明，咁都係返大灣區生活比較適合！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191014/large/1570982740_8a54.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191014%2Flarge%2F1570982740_8a54.gif&h=1d4aa207&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n普通口罩升級到防毒面具。<br />\n<br />\n八方當然係真‧香港人，所以做咗測試，老實講啲圖唔係全部一睇就明，但越睇越欷歔，例如6月時香港人仲會着唔同色衫，但到10月全黑black bloc已經係指定服裝；之前只戴普通口罩，現時已升級到防毒面具；6月初明明只係要求撤回惡法，但今日已變咗六大訴求，新增埋解散警隊，口號亦由「香港人加油」變成「香港人反抗」；「自殺」個案亦較6月時大增，交通工具選擇上，就已經冇咗黨鐵了。至於壓軸一幅，係777個鼻本來已變長，家陣就長到打蛇餅，即係佢呢幾個月又講咗數之不盡嘅大話囉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191014/large/1570982741_1364.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191014%2Flarge%2F1570982741_1364.gif&h=3ffd2fb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n口號由加油變反抗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191014/large/1570982741_53ca.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191014%2Flarge%2F1570982741_53ca.gif&h=aa27a5ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n交通工具選擇上，冇咗黨鐵了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191014/large/1570982742_1413.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191014%2Flarge%2F1570982742_1413.gif&h=0e4f3cd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林鄭數月間個鼻長咗幾倍。<br />\n<br />\n十幅圖雖然想用輕鬆手法喚醒大家面對抗爭，但巴絲們唔太受落，有人留言話「內容農場級質素，笑唔出」，亦有人反建議去創意台而非新聞台開post。不過，按照不分化不割席不譴責原則，雖然唔完美，技術亦有待改善，但算係可以接受啦，手足們，大家繼續爬山啦！<br />\n<br />\n李八方 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n江湖滾熱辣 (尊子)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n隔牆有耳： 太子站慶生  片中人認衰︰行為愚蠢會反思 (李八方)"}]}